 182:../../Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_rcc.c ****   *            - All interrupts disabled
 183:../../Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_rcc.c ****   * @note   This function doesn't modify the configuration of the
